Deprecated API

Deprecated Classes
com.taursys.xml.render.AttributeTextFieldRenderer
          The AttributeTextFieldRender is no longer used. Attributes are now rendered using an AttributeRenderer. 
com.taursys.xml.render.TextFieldRenderer
          The TextFieldRender is no longer used. A TextField now contains a TextNode which uses a TextNodeRenderer.

          The TextFieldRender is no longer used. A TextField now contains a TextNode which uses a TextNodeRenderer.
